text: ila anu: "Ayana mi painundi gani, leda mi padala krindi nundi gani, mipai apada avatarimpa jeyagala samarthyam kaligi unnadu; mariyu mim'malni tegalu tegaluga cesi, paraspara kalahala ruci cupa galige (sakti kuda) kaligi unnadu." Cudu! Bahusa varu (satyanni) grahistaromonani, memu e vidhanga ma sucanalanu vividha rupalalo vivaristunnamo
